    "text": [
        "Dear Amie,",
        "Hope you're well. Did you find the job that you were looking for? I'm just writing to let you know that I'm coming to Switzerland next month, and I really hope you can join me on my trip.",
        "Do you remember, we had a blast last year! However, I can't really recall the exact date of my visit. Actually, I've to mention the details in my visa application form, and since your memory is far better than mine, I thought you'll help me.",
        "You'll be glad to know that I'm planning a holiday in Engelberg, a town in Switzerland, which is just about a hundred miles from your home. I've heard about the very famous Mount Titlis, I'd surely go there. Can you suggest some other tourist attractions?",
        "Although I was thinking of a solo trip earlier, I thought I'll enjoy even more with you. You've always been my partner in crime! So, I really hope you can join me for a weekend. Because my brother-in-law is so understanding, I'm sure he can excuse you for just 3 days, and that much you can do for your little sister. I'll share with you the itinerary later via an e-mail.",
        "Hoping to see you soon!",
        "Warm wishes,",
        "Katie"
